<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/vendor/bootstrap-icons/font/bootstrap-icons.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/vendor/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css' />
    <script src="/stylesheets/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/themes.js" id="theme-script"></script>
    <script type="module" src="/js/help.js" id="help-script"></script>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href={{ icon }} />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href={{ icon }}>
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href={{ icon }} type="image/x-icon">
    <!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->
    <script async src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-L1RDBDQQLX"></script>
    <script>
        window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];
        function gtag() { dataLayer.push(arguments); }
        gtag('js', new Date());
        gtag('config', 'G-L1RDBDQQLX');

        // Verzögerte Weiterleitung nach 6 Sekunden
        setTimeout(() => {
            window.location.href = "https://waerchzigchastu.tools/";
        }, 6000);
    </script>
    <style>
        .redirect-container {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            height: 100vh;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .loader {
            border: 8px solid #f3f3f3;
            border-top: 8px solid #d40037;
            border-radius: 50%;
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            animation: spin 1s linear infinite;
            margin: 20px;
        }

        @keyframes spin {
            0% { transform: rotate(0deg); }
            100% { transform: rotate(360deg); }
        }

        .url-box {
            background: #222;
            padding: 10px 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-family: monospace;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body class="p-3 m-0 border-0 bd-example m-0 border-0" data-bs-theme="dark">
    <div class="redirect-container">
        <h1>Unser Intranet ist umgezogen</h1>
        <p>Sie werden in wenigen Sekunden automatisch weitergeleitet.</p>
        <p><strong>Bitte speichern Sie sich die neue Seite ab, damit Sie künftig direkt darauf zugreifen können:</strong></p>
        <div class="url-box">
            <a href="https://waerchzigchastu.tools/" style="color: #d40037;">https://waerchzigchastu.tools/</a>
        </div>
        <div class="loader"></div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
